ai|publisher=Ticketmaster|date=28 November 2018|accessdate=4 January 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105043007/https://blog.ticketmaster.co.uk/new-music/new-music-slowthai-41822|archive-date=5 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"vevo\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8486400/ybn-crew-slowthai-2019-vevo-artists-to-watch-exclusive|title=YBN Crew & Slowthai Make Debuts as First 2019 Vevo Artists To Watch: Exclusive|publisher=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|date=26 November 2018|accessdate=4 January 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190101131821/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8486400/ybn-crew-slowthai-2019-vevo-artists-to-watch-exclusive|archive-date=1 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Vevo]]\n| DSCVR 2019 Artists To Watch\n|-\n| [[BBC]]\n| [[Sound of...|Sound of 2019]]\n| {{nom|Fourth}}<ref name=\"soundof2019\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-46705455|title=Slowthai: From Northampton to South Africa|publisher=[[BBC]]|date=8 January 2019|accessdate=8 January 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190108093135/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-46705455|archive-date=8 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[DIY (magazine)|DIY]]\n| Class of 2019\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{included}}<br/><ref name=\"diy\">{{cite web|url=http://diymag.com/2018/12/13/class-of-2019-slowthai-interview|title=CLASS OF 2019: SLOWTHAI|publisher=[[DIY (magazine)|DIY]]|date=13 December 2018|accessdate=4 January 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104230951/http://diymag.com/2018/12/13/class-of-2019-slowthai-interview|archive-date=4 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"metro\">{{cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/12/29/ones-to-watch-2019-sam-fender-ella-mai-and-slowthai-lead-eclectic-mix-of-artists-into-the-new-year-8262106/|title=Ones To Watch 2019: Sam Fender, Ella Mai and Slowthai lead eclectic mix of artists into the new year|publisher