{"title_page": "Unit 999", "text_new": "{{refimprove|date=January 2013}}\n{{Infobox military unit\n| unit_name                     = Unit 999\n| native_name                   = \u0627\u0644\u0648\u062d\u062f\u0629 999 \u0642\u062a\u0627\u0644\n| image                         = \n| caption                       = \n| Motto                         = Victory or Martyrdom\n| dates                         = \n| country                       = [[Egypt]]\n| allegiance                    = [[Military of Egypt]]\n| command_structure             = [[Sa'ka Forces|Thunderbolt]]\n| branch                        = [[Egyptian Army]]\n| type                          = [[Special Operations Forces]]\n| role                          = [[Special operations]]<br>[[reconnaissance]]\n| specialization                = |\n| size                          = Classified\n| garrison                      = [[Cairo|Southern Cairo]]\n| current_commander             = Classified\n| nickname                      = \n| motto                         = \n| colors                        = \n| march                         = \n| mascot                        = The Eagle of Thunderbolt\n| battles                       = Classified\n| notable_commanders            = \n| anniversaries                 = \n| identification_symbol         = <!-- Aircraft -->\n| aircraft_helicopter           = Classified\n}}\n\n'''Unit 999''' (Arabic: \u0627\u0644\u0648\u062d\u062f\u0629 999 \u0642\u062a\u0627\u0644), also known as ''Task Force 999'', is an [[Egypt]]ian [[Military of Egypt|military]] [[special operations]] and [[reconnaissance]] unit.\n\n==See also==\n* [[Unit 777]]\n* [[Unit 333]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{egypt-stub}}\n{{mil-unit-stub}}{{Egyptian Army}}\n[[Category:Special forces of Egypt]]\n", "text_old": "{{refimprove|date=January 2013}}\n{{Infobox military unit\n|unit_name   = Unit 999 Combat\n|native_name = \u0627\u0644\u0648\u062d\u062f\u0629 999 \u0642\u062a\u0627\u0644\n|image       = \n|